{"body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"schemename\">\n<span id=\"id1\"></span><h1>schemeName</h1>\n<p>Extracts the value of the request Uri scheme.</p>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"signature\">\n<h2>Signature</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight-scala\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span class=\"k\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">schemeName</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Directive1</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">String</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> \n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"description\">\n<h2>Description</h2>\n<p>The <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">schemeName</span></tt> directive can be used to determine the Uri scheme (i.e. &#8220;http&#8221;, &#8220;https&#8221;, etc.)\nfor an incoming request.</p>\n<p>For rejecting a request if it doesn&#8217;t match a specified scheme name, see the <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../scheme/#scheme\"><em>scheme</em></a> directive.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"example\">\n<h2>Example</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight-scala\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span class=\"k\">val</span> <span class=\"n\">route</span> <span class=\"k\">=</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">schemeName</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span> <span class=\"n\">scheme</span> <span class=\"k\">=&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">complete</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;The scheme is &#39;${scheme}&#39;&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"nc\">Get</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;https://www.example.com/&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">~&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">route</span> <span class=\"o\">~&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">check</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">responseAs</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">String</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">===</span> <span class=\"s\">&quot;The scheme is &#39;https&#39;&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n", "display_toc": true, "title": "schemeName", "sourcename": "", "customsidebar": null, "current_page_name": "documentation/spray-routing/scheme-directives/schemeName", "next": {"link": "../../security-directives/", "title": "SecurityDirectives"}, "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["documentation/spray-routing/security-directives/index", "SecurityDirectives", "N", "next"], ["documentation/spray-routing/scheme-directives/scheme", "scheme", "P", "previous"]], "meta": {}, "parents": [{"link": "../../../", "title": "Documentation"}, {"link": "../../", "title": "spray-routing"}, {"link": "../../predefined-directives-by-trait/", "title": "Predefined Directives (by trait)"}, {"link": "../", "title": "SchemeDirectives"}], "sidebars": null, "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">schemeName</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#signature\">Signature</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#description\">Description</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#example\">Example</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n", "prev": {"link": "../scheme/", "title": "scheme"}, "metatags": ""}